> > > > > Make the check as simple as "test_type == TEST_HUGETLB" because that's the
> > > > > only mem that doesn't support ZEROPAGE.
> > > > > 
> > > > > Signed-off-by: Peter Xu <peterx@redhat.com>
> > > > > ---
> > > > >   tools/testing/selftests/mm/userfaultfd.c | 2 +-
